{"id": 1685, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些碎片时间对你来说其实比整块时间还好用？", "description": "我一般是，整块时间摸鱼，碎片时间抓紧干正事。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2444, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170512155927Uje0tI6vMHcAos3J.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-25T03:00:49Z", "options": [{"id": 207360, "content": "哄完孩子睡下，自己洗漱完，躺在床上的那点时间才是属于自己的碎片时间，可以看点自己喜欢的文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040275}, {"id": 207361, "content": "睡觉前背英语单词 既背会了单词，又提高了睡眠质量", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037993}, {"id": 207362, "content": "在地铁上看书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 62517}, {"id": 207875, "content": "没事去操场打打球。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991291}, {"id": 207364, "content": "上厕所的那个  我是吃饭的时候看好奇心文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974719}, {"id": 207365, "content": "课间休息，午休等室友吃完饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652800}, {"id": 207877, "content": "坐车的时候刷微博！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004349}, {"id": 207366, "content": "比如说那些再也不想重现的囧情o(╯□╰)o有次拉肚子，没到厕所已经出状况了，结果裤子完蛋了。用了近整包手帕纸巾才勉强清理在裤档里的“屎”，还担心出去会有奇怪的味道？！???‍???❎??", "image": "img/option/option/20170525225357i9GFtPo0Xpz2UKvb", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75248}, {"id": 207882, "content": "中午吃外卖时是一天最享受的时刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 207883, "content": "早上回公司地铁里可以了解世界大事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 208907, "content": "睡觉前刷了很多知乎。考前两个小时，复习了一门课", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001890}, {"id": 207373, "content": "当然是坐地铁的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037240}, {"id": 207630, "content": "多长时间以内才算碎片时间？我80%的纸书是在地铁里的半小时看完", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038683}, {"id": 207887, "content": "洗澡的时候追剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041909}, {"id": 207376, "content": "大清早五六点起来干活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034967}, {"id": 207377, "content": "碎片时间用来听听音乐放松下节奏比较有用，如果用来做一些系统性的学习效果比较差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030129}, {"id": 207634, "content": "临睡前，总感觉有忙不完的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033460}, {"id": 207379, "content": "都是在上厕所时看得好奇心。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628049}, {"id": 207381, "content": "击鼓端午", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040342}, {"id": 207383, "content": "睡觉之前玩手机的时候 心特别静 看什么都记得很清楚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907451}, {"id": 207384, "content": "高铁地铁这种开得稳的最适合看书工作了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040366}, {"id": 207640, "content": "等餐的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038127}, {"id": 207897, "content": "地铁上背单词", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 207386, "content": "等开会或和领导协商事情间隙可以快速把接下来要做的事情列一下。经验上来说会比回去之后理得清楚。", "image": "img/option/option/201705260008349PypiCdA4YSnwGEo", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039950}, {"id": 221211, "content": "蹲坑的时候看书贼专心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076971}, {"id": 207389, "content": "刷手机的时间用来用心看申论?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040376}, {"id": 207649, "content": "洗澡的时候敷面膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040981}, {"id": 207396, "content": "考试复习的时候先花大把正常作息时间去做学习前准备比如玩手机，然后利用深夜熬夜看书比如现在的我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034023}, {"id": 207399, "content": "一边洗衣服一边看剧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009270}, {"id": 207400, "content": "上班下班都在工作的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922119}, {"id": 207401, "content": "因为是做快消品，每个便利店必须呆10几分钟，于是在便利店用手机翻译了几篇MOOC，还学了乐理……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095135}, {"id": 207402, "content": "因为是做快消品，每个便利店必须呆10几分钟，于是在便利店用手机翻译了几篇MOOC，还学了乐理……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095135}, {"id": 207658, "content": "乘地铁，飞机，高铁的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940580}, {"id": 207404, "content": "工作技能好多时候都是零碎的时候学的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181086}, {"id": 207661, "content": "上厕所……等车……吃早饭……睡觉前", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038442}, {"id": 207406, "content": "平时都忙着处理公司事情，碎片时间正好写几行代码....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871069}, {"id": 207662, "content": "吃饭的时候，听新闻；看书时，听音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040958}, {"id": 207663, "content": "啊……一个很重要，无聊的大课的时候，我用了几个星期的大课时间居然啃完了《1984》……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038442}, {"id": 207409, "content": "碎片时间想一天工作安排……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747138}, {"id": 207411, "content": "厕所，等车/飞机，公共交通上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020839}, {"id": 207412, "content": "每天晚上洗澡之前的那段时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040474}, {"id": 207413, "content": "失眠就听听力，听着听着就睡着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690035}, {"id": 207414, "content": "课间十分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984869}, {"id": 211254, "content": "睡前三小时，会突然想起很多想要做的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001162}, {"id": 207415, "content": "开会的时候，默默的看小说。下班时候倒不太想看，开会时候却看的津津有味。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814708}, {"id": 207416, "content": "厕所时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812813}, {"id": 203065, "content": "搬到离公司更远的地方，通勤的时候竟然多看了很多书", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 203066, "content": "下班回家也是葛优瘫，发现不如到家前在小区旁边空地多溜达几分钟，放松效果更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 207418, "content": "嗯，吃饭的时候看奇葩说，经常笑到喷饭?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026622}, {"id": 207674, "content": "跑步的时候刚好听完一集逻辑思维", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819601}]}